document.full_text: an explosion early wednesday on a gas pipeline in the sinai cut supplies of egyptian natural gas to israel for the second time this year, in a suspected act of sabotage.
document.title: pipeline blast in sinai, said to be sabotage, cuts gas supply in israel and jordan
